      <div class="flow" role="img" aria-label="Flowchart: start, ask if only one instance makes sense, branch yes to ask if global access needed, branch yes to Singleton, no branches lead to alternatives">
        <div class="flow-box">Does the resource <em>logically</em> need only one instance?</div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="flow-branch">
