<div class="container">
<section id="about">
  <h2>Live Singleton State</h2>
  <p>
    The panel below reflects the internal state of the <code>ThemeManager</code>
    singleton in real time. Every toggle click updates the single shared instance —
    no other object can create a second one.
  </p>

  <div class="state-panel">
    <div class="state-item">
      <span class="state-label">Instance ID</span>
      <span class="state-value" id="instanceId">—</span>
    </div>
